# =============================================================================
# === Upstream clone bulk — only ATOM-specific files are tracked            ===
# =============================================================================

# atom-llm: LiteLLM is a PyPI dependency — only our extensions/config live here
atom-llm/*
!atom-llm/atom_extensions/
!atom-llm/atom_extensions/**
!atom-llm/main.py
!atom-llm/Dockerfile
!atom-llm/Dockerfile.dev
!atom-llm/config.dev.yaml
!atom-llm/UPSTREAM_DIFF.md
!atom-llm/LICENSE
!atom-llm/CLAUDE.md

# agentscope-based clones: keep src/ (ATOM modifications); drop CI/docs/tests
